org.jetel.util.classloader

Class GreedyURLClassLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader
      • java.security.SecureClassLoader
        • java.net.URLClassLoader
          • org.jetel.util.classloader.GreedyURLClassLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, ClassDefinitionFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PluginClassLoader

    public class GreedyURLClassLoader
extends java.net.URLClassLoader
implements ClassDefinitionFactory
    Class-loader extended from URL classloader which by default loads classes and finds resources (greedily) from specified URLs at first. If unsuccessful, it tries to load class or to find resource using parent classloader. Specified packages are excluded from greedy class loading. On the other hand, class loader can behave like ordinary class loader and only the specified packages are loaded greedily.
